Hi again FPSBanana! Now i'm back with a brand new map called: De_Swamps!

Its a bomb/defuse map but not as you know them...

T's Object: Protect your self against the CT force at all cost! Plant the bomb and blow your self up!

CT's Object: Eliminate all T's at all cost! Get to the bomb (if planted) and defuse it!

Enjoy the map & Rate it after having tryed it!
